question: Within a radius of 150 kilometers, where can I find  a fast food restaurant along the way to the Contemporary Austin - Jones Center, Austin, TX from Five Wells Roping Rodeo Arena, TX?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-97.402227 30.995182)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-97.742825 30.26925)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'fast_food'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-97.402227 30.995182)',4326)::geography, 150000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-97.402227 30.995182)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
